  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So what happened-- we had-- we had one room with one [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] bed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I decided that in the bed will sleep Sula with the child, who is Zarek.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rachela slept somewhere on the floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dora and her two children slept on the other place on the floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was in the rocker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The next day, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was Sunday.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we tried to organize, you know, ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But by the middle of the day, another order came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Those who worked in proper places, go to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I-- we went to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I returned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we brought-- you see, we brought along some food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the moment, we even didn't think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there was such a chaos, you know, like a Tower of Babel, you know, people going here and there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Children were lost, parents separated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It is hard to-- from the city, they used to-- some carts used to bring cripples, sick.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Where to put-- they used to throw them right on the floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then came-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of course, there was organized-- I don't want to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I can tell only one thing, that the Judenrat was leftist whereas the police was Betarist.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were-- great many of my students from both schools, from all the schools, from the private school where I used to teach and from former [NON-ENGLISH] school, Tarbut.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They start to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, when we went to work, so, in a day or two-- so the first days, you know, we were so confused that I even don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
